HAPPY BIRTHDAY TWINNIE 💐🤍🫶
__________________________________________________
Happy birthday to my lovely brother, the calmness to my werey, thank you for always being there for me, for being my best friend, for always having my back, for taking all my problems as your own, for praying for me and with me, for making me have one of the best years yet, for showing me what unconditional love is. I pray that all your heart desires be granted this year, and whatever you decide to do, you prosper. I pray that before you ask for anything, you will receive. May this year be your easiest year yet, may lines fall into pleasant places for you, may you receive favor from your friends, your competitors, everyone around you. Just as you are always cheerful and seeing the positive in everything, I pray that joy and happiness never leaves you, you will not have any reason to question God’s blessings in your life. Anywhere you step foot in this year, you will possess. God bless you. I love you ❤️💕 
___________________________________________________
🎶 Brother @kodaline
